I read this un-finished to a couple LJ users this weekend and told them I'd get back to them so...


It wasn't her imagination
the sounds behind her.
Her hair pulled back
in a make-shift ponytail
his hand the rubber band.
The words came out
She knew they were heard.
All through high school
they said she could
wake the dead.
Now lying here...
   Will the echos?

so guys better worse?  What do you think?

nerp

Let me catch everyone who doesnt know whats up, up.  My life has been the very normal- Wake up (maybe), work (most defiantly), sleep (in necessary). untill...

It seems that my boring solitaire life may be ending.  A young woman has com into my life and is showing intrest unlike any one before, and the weird thing is Im interested in her as well.  This doesn't happen to often, but I don't want to get my hopes up than have them dashed on the jagged rocks of reality.

keepin you in the loop,
Nerp

I went to bed last night with a headache and never got any sleep, I got to the point I was almost in tears because I could not get to sleep.  Now I am awake at ten o clock at night and still fighting a splitting headache.  For those of you who don't know me when I get tired I get reflective, when I get reflective I get depressive, when I get depressive I get tired.  So know I have repeated that cycle about nine times today and am wanting to call 'Her' knowing her voice will make me feel better, but also knowing I cant because she is part of the reason I'm depressed.  I've gone through my short list of friends and cant find anyone to chat with to take my mind off the pain in my head and my heart so I thought I'd just post a little wine on the journal, sorry to waste your time.

God bless,
Nerp

You're Sudan!
Every time you get a headache, you reach for some aspirin, only to realize that someone destroyed it.  That's just how things are going for you right now... it's hard to eat, hard to sleep, hard to not have a headache.  You try to relax, but people always jump on you about something that doesn't make sense.  If you were a goat, you'd be a Nubian.

Well I was right about the talk... I know I said to diffrent things.  Well one was just a dream, the other reality.  She told me her and the other guy were going to step it up, now let me say this about that.  She not one time during our talk say his name, and only brought him up a few times, I found that odd.  I have begun to move on but after spending the better part of the last seven months with her in some way or the other I have a long hard road ahead.  

I miss you starsdistorted

good day
God bless
good night
Nerp

I'm tired of the run around, I'm tired of the crap.  I'm tired of not being happy all the time.  I'm tired.

Love ya all
Nerp
Im tired, and I have a Theater test today, I have a friend whom I love wanting me to do somethin.  I have a few stories to post but most of then take a few

i envy the fog
it comes on suddenly
demanding attention
it lingers impacting all
it leaves, no one is sadden
no one will cry every one knows
fog comes and goes
why cant i just blow away, 
no one should cry, no one should be sad
i envy the fog

griping cold steal
finger twitches
one inch
hammer falls
pin hits its mark
a spark
a contained explosion
no where to go but out
rifling leaves ridges
lead traverses the distance
faster then the wind
impact
finger twitches
one inch one life
how much longer do we have

Why would I put something down telling you I've got something to tell you, but not just wrtie what I want to tell you.  Well Im not finished puting it all together, but I will say this as of right now Im on cloud 9.9.

It has been a few days, that just goes to show you how much my life sucks.  Even hitting the highlights all you get is crap, so I guess today cant be much worse than every day before it.  Last night I did something alot of my friends would be mad at me for, but I cant help it.  They think I should leave her alone but she is like a drug the longer Im away from her the wrose I feel and then just the sound of her voice can send me on a high.  I dont care who I piss off, I'm happy with her and if anyonr has a problem with it they can... Well they can die mad or get over it.  I just found out my favorite animated movie is coming out on DVD on tuesday it's called 'the Point' every one needs to see it and youll see why I love it so much.  Ohwell Im done now I just felt like pinging the radar, let you know Im alive and reading even if nothing ever really hapens to me.

"Come Sit With Me On the Beach"

You're the person everyone can depend on to keep a
level head in a tough situation. You tend to
withdraw to quiet places like your room or a
favorite outdoor area when things get too
hectic. You rarely get angry or worked up about
anything, but when you do, you've thought it
through and have decided that it's worth it.
Things like stubbed toes and burnt toast have
never fazed you, and neither do relationship
problems with friends. Since no one has a
reason to be angry with you, you're always the
one people go to for advice, and you're always
willing to offer it. People are attracted to
you because you always seem a bit mysterious to
them due to your quiet, reserved nature. Once
they get to know you, they are in awe of your
wisdom and sense of peace.

I just got back form the Linkin Park Meteora Tour, at Alltel Arena.  This makes my third 'Big' show, Chili Peppers/ Foo Fighters, than Aerosmith/ Fuel tonight it was, Story of the Year, Hoobastank, P.O.D. and Linkin Park.  The show rocked all save Hoobastank I mean Hoob-astunk.  They Played their songs great, but that is all they did, it was like listing to their CD and looking at a picture of them.  I'm glad I didn't pay to see them play.  Also I sat next to a young lady named Laura, who was quite captivating.  I had a hard time getting her to loosen up she seemed a little shy and timid, but after I had successfully made a complete full of my self a few times she seemed to open up.  I got her number... at least she says it is her number.  for all I know it could be the number to her pyscho boyfriend who is waiting for me to call so he can trace my call and rip my lips off.

The young lady who caused such a problem with the Phone the other night, is now I feel about to cause a problem yet again.  I believe she is going to chase after a very close friend of mine who is inetrested in her, but she is not sure if she likes him.  Knowing her like I do that means when the relationship goes from friends to 'lovers' she will try and back out. So do I talk to my guy friend or do I stay out of it and hope for the best?

PS I dont think you should go after him.  You know who Im taking about.
